## Testing

### Unit Tests
1. Run `npm test` or `yarn test` to execute unit tests.

### End-to-End Tests
1. Run `npm run test:e2e` or `yarn test:e2e` to execute end-to-end tests.

## API Requests
1. Install the REST client extension for VSCode.
2. Open the `request.rest` file provided in the project.
3. Click on each request to open it.
4. Click on the "Send Request" button at the top right corner of each request to send it.
5. The response will be displayed below the request.

## Running the Server
1. Set the `NODE_ENV` environment variable to `test`.
2. Run `npm start` or `yarn start` to start the server in the test environment.

